comment: Antetokounmpo (MIL) cleanly strips the ball from Batum (CHA).
Monroe (MIL) does not affect Walker's (CHA) RSBQ at the start of the drive.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Bayless (MIL) and firms up, giving him room to avoid the contact.
RHH shows that Monroe (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Walker (CHA) that does not affect his layup attempt.
L-Slash and RATR shows that Antetokounmpo (MIL) cleanly blocks Batum's (CHA) shot attempt. Any body contact that occurs after the block is considered incidental.
Batum (CHA) makes body contact with Bayless (MIL) that affects his RSBQ and causes him to fall to the floor.
Lamb (CHA) and Mayo (MIL) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Bayless (MIL) obtains a legal guarding position prior to the contact with Walker (CHA).
Mayo (MIL) commits a take foul on Walker (CHA).
